{"tid":2157226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方稱死亡無可疑 男子除剩底褲 斷兩手指倒梯間傷重亡","createTime":"2020-08-15T01:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T08:12:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10407403318eb46181d508f40e7eb79e5f0f3b0d","tid":2157226,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200815/H2CFNRTM6BH6TIRZ6APJBRKD7E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200815%2FH2CFNRTM6BH6TIRZ6APJBRKD7E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8YD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=82be84ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200815%2FH2CFNRTM6BH6TIRZ6APJBRKD7E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fa37ab73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200815/H2CFNRTM6BH6TIRZ6APJBRKD7E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n男子除剩底褲 斷兩手指倒梯間傷重亡<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n【07:15】死者姓范41歲，送院搶救延至凌晨5時15分死亡，警員在其單位內發現遺書，案件初步並無可疑，死因有待法醫檢驗。據悉事主有不良嗜好。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗鴨寮街208號一幢舊樓，凌晨3時許，一名僅穿着內褲的男子，手部受傷呆坐在大廈近地下梯間位置，街坊經過大驚報警。傷者右手無名指及中指失去，其後陷入昏迷，救護員趕至將他送院搶救，惟終告不治。探員封鎖現場，展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場梯間有血迹，對開行人路有傷者的長褲，稍後警員在大廈5、6樓梯間及傷者住所單位，先後發現一柄染血菜刀，及撿回男子無名指及中指送院進行接駁，初步相信男子自殘受傷。現場消息稱，他疑有不良嗜好，懷疑受藥物影響致神情失常，拿起菜刀斬手自殘。"},{"pid":"32037a947e2f3885a826141dcdfb7443d5366c5b","tid":2157226,"uid":44559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:56:18.000Z","msg":"斬手指介賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db89cf